Package net.ssehub.comani.analysis.variabilitychange.diff

This package contains all classes for analyzing the Commits.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildFileDiff
    This class implements analysis methods and required attributes for counting the changes made to a build file (Make).

    In particular, this class differentiates between changed lines containing general build information and lines that contain variability information, e.g.
    DiffAnalyzer
    This class implements a general diff analyzer.

    This class is used to provide the numbers of changed lines in different file types of a specific commit.
    FileDiff
    This abstract class represents a general file diff.
    ModelFileDiff
    This class implements analysis methods and required attributes for counting the changes made to a model file (Kconfig).

    In particular, this class differentiates between changed lines containing general model elements, e.g.
    OtherFileDiff
    This class is used to count changes to other files than model, source code, or build files.
    SourceFileDiff
    This class implements analysis methods and required attributes for counting the changes made to a source file (C-family).

    In particular, this class differentiates between changed lines containing general source code and lines that contain variability information, e.g.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FileDiff.FileType
    Enumeration for defining the type of file diff for a specific object.

Package net.ssehub.comani.analysis.variabilitychange.diff Description

This package contains all classes for analyzing the Commits. Use DiffAnalyzer class to start an analysis.
Author:
Christian Kroeher
